metadata.name: Outskirts #1/10
metadata.description:
The outer edge of the city, the edges of a community. A metaphor for the border between the known and unknown, where the familiar and unfamiliar meet.

Artwork created with pure code in p5js with a composition dictated by random Cellular Automata rules. 

With the exception of a few restrictions, the machine played a crucial role in crafting this glitchy landscape.
